Installation:
- Put TimeTrail.jar in your bukkit plugins folder.

Sign layout:
   [TimeTrail]  <--- Not case sensitive
    Trackname   <--- Case sensitive
    Begin/End   <--- Not case sensitive

Permissions:
- TimeTrail.create -- Allows players to create TimeTrail tracks.
- TimeTrail.use -- Allows players to use TimeTrail tracks.
- TimeTrail.* -- Does both

If PermissionsEx/bPermissions is not detected only OPs can make tracks and everyone can use them.